# .gcloudignore
# Deterministic Cloud Run source builds from repo root.

.git
**/.DS_Store

# Never ship local deps / outputs
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dist-types
**/build
**/coverage
**/.expo
**/ios/build
**/android/build

# Never ship secrets
.env
.env.*

# --- Allowlist the actual build context we need for root deploy ---
!package.json
!package-lock.json
!tsconfig.json
!Dockerfile
!scripts/**

# Canonical contracts package (single source of truth)
!lib/contracts/**
# (Allow other lib files only if you actually need them; safe default is include all lib)
!lib/**

# API service source
!services/api/**
# Functions can remain excluded if you want smaller contexts, but safe to include:
!services/functions/**